      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Secure land tenure is an important condition of healthy urban growth. It is typical that, once residents have clear ownership of their land, they will continue to invest in their self-built house. Also in the case where a basic house unit is already built, owners will continue to maintain and upgrade it. This is the way that cities have evolved historically, with piecemeal additions and gradual improvement of house components with more permanent materials.",
      "id": "10094898567866"
